1
00:00:30,450 --> 00:00:31,766
Lady Rinkham...

2
00:00:32,860 --> 00:00:33,784
Rinkham...

3
00:00:36,220 --> 00:00:37,113
My Lady?

4
00:00:38,300 --> 00:00:40,006
Where are you?

5
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:43,716
Rinkham.

6
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:45,323
Are you looking for me?

7
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:49,292
Hey you!

8
00:00:50,100 --> 00:00:51,396
What on earth are you doing up there?

9
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:53,040
Come down this instant!

10
00:00:54,130 --> 00:00:55,403
If you want me to come down,

11
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:57,218
why don't you climb up and help me?

12
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:02,387
Do you have any idea how stubborn you are?

13
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,400
If you fall,

14
00:01:04,436 --> 00:01:06,800
Luang Wisanu will surely punish me severely.

15
00:01:07,770 --> 00:01:10,609
Please come down before you get hurt.

16
00:01:12,467 --> 00:01:12,923
Oh!!

17
00:01:14,190 --> 00:01:16,080
I was just teasing you.

18
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,624
I'm perfectly fine.

19
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:21,033
Then please, enjoy playing by yourself.

20
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:23,483
Wait a moment, Kaew!

21
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,864
I told you that you shouldn't do things like this.

22
00:01:45,895 --> 00:01:48,455
I warned you to be careful, or something bad would happen.

23
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,424
Alright, alright, alright.

24
00:01:50,449 --> 00:01:51,723
I get it.

25
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,341
I guess your ankle might be sprained.

26
00:02:07,130 --> 00:02:09,963
It is, but...

27
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,987
No "buts" from now on.

28
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,375
You must listen to me and me alone,

29
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:17,464
so you won't get hurt again.

30
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,886
Fine.

31
00:02:21,747 --> 00:02:23,740
I will heed your warnings more closely from now on.

32
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,596
Now... will you help me already?

33
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,981
I’ll go find someone to give you a massage.

34
00:03:22,830 --> 00:03:23,587
No!!

35
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,590
I don't want my dad to find out.

36
00:03:27,587 --> 00:03:29,132
Can you do it for me instead?

37
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,507
Thanks.

38
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,550
But even if you help me,

39
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,215
I’m not going to stop teasing you, you know.

40
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:33,476
As long as you don't play around and get yourself hurt again,

41
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:38,664
I’ll let you tease me as much as you want.

42
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,393
Are you afraid of the thunder?

43
00:05:00,340 --> 00:05:03,600
Close your eyes, you won't be scared anymore.

44
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:09,476
I’m not scared.

45
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,735
Just startled, that’s all.

46
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:17,901
Even if you aren't scared, just close your eyes.

47
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:24,153
You sound like you're giving me an order.

48
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:28,160
Well, I am your bodyguard.

49
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,590
Fine,

50
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:35,895
I'll listen to you just this once.

51
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:25,403
When you're all out of mischief,

52
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,590
you're actually pretty cute.

53
00:06:57,650 --> 00:06:58,713
You weren't asleep.

54
00:06:59,290 --> 00:07:00,301
I know it.

55
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,024
You're still awake?

56
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,270
Well, someone was touching me all night.

57
00:07:20,090 --> 00:07:20,769
I…

58
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:23,686
I…

59
00:07:26,978 --> 00:07:28,363
Like this?

60
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:37,040
Have you ever been this close to another woman?

61
00:07:40,929 --> 00:07:42,141
Never.

62
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,058
Then…

63
00:07:45,890 --> 00:07:47,243
I am your first.

64
00:07:57,140 --> 00:07:58,350
This isn't right.

65
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,009
I am merely a guard.

66
00:08:02,806 --> 00:08:04,166
I don't care about that.

67
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,206
The truth is…

68
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:20,289
there is something you might not know yet.

69
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:26,307
Perhaps I already know.

70
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:31,440
But you don't have to tell me right now.

71
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:37,089
I will wait until you are ready.

72
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:41,132
Because to me,

73
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:49,852
who you are doesn't matter as much as what we feel for each other...

74
00:08:53,850 --> 00:08:55,083
...right now.

75
00:11:02,580 --> 00:11:03,495
You’re awake?

76
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,406
Did you get any sleep?

77
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,606
I did.

78
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:18,418
I slept quite well,

79
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,190
actually… after last night.

80
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:24,270
Are you leaving already?

81
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:27,833
Rinkham,

82
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,803
open the door for me.
